olid #eee;\">\n            Nettoyage superficiel, sans action cibl&eacute;e sur la racine\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding: 14px; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; color: #333; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;\">\n            Densit&eacute; &amp; volume per&ccedil;us\n          </td>\n          <td style=\"padding: 14px; color: #8A4B2D; font-weight: 700; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; background-color: #F5EDE7;\">\n            Biotine pour soutenir une chevelure visuellement plus dense\n          </td>\n          <td style=\"padding: 14px; color: #999; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;\">\n            Peut alourdir ou laisser les cheveux plats\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding: 14px; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; color: #333; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;\">\n            Cuir chevelu &amp; fr&eacute;quence des lavages\n          </td>\n          <td style=\"padding: 14px; color: #8A4B2D; font-weight: 700; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; background-color: #F5EDE7;\">\n            Nettoyant aux acides amin&eacute;s, sans sulfates &mdash; respecte le cuir chevelu\n          </td>\n          <td style=\"padding: 14px; color: #999; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;\">\n            Sulfates fr&eacute;quents, peut irriter ou ass&eacute;cher\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding: 14px; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; color: #333;\">\n            Composition &amp; respect du cuir chevelu\n          </td>\n          <td style=\"padding: 14px; color: #8A4B2D; font-weight: 700; background-color: #F5EDE7;\">\n            Formule 100% d&eacute;taill&eacute;e&nbsp;: romarin, k&eacute;ratine hydrolys&eacute;e, biotine &mdash; sans sulfates ni parab&egrave;nes\n          </td>\n          <td style=\"padding: 14px; color: #999;\">\n            Tensioactifs parfois agressifs, silicones fr&eacute;quents\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </